{indented_block(rules)}

        ## Workflow

        - Planning trigger: {spec["workflow"]["planningTrigger"]}
        - Implementation focus: {spec["workflow"]["implementationFocus"]}

        ### Review Checklist

{indented_block(review)}

        ### Handoffs

{indented_block(bullet_lines([f"{handoff['from']} -> {handoff['to']}: {', '.join(handoff['expects'])}" for handoff in spec["handoffs"]], "Add handoffs in `init-orch.md`."))}

        ### Response Style

{indented_block(response_style_overview(response_style))}

        #### Style Rules

{indented_block(bullet_lines(response_style["rules"], "Add responseStyle.rules in `init-orch.md`."))}

        #### Example Replies

{indented_block(bullet_lines(response_style["examples"], "Add responseStyle.examples in `init-orch.md`."))}

        ### Verification

{indented_block(verification)}

        ## Skills

{indented_block(skills)}

